  "title": "Groundnut germplasm seed viability after ten years of storage as base collection.",
  "abstract": "This paper covers the changes in seed germination capability of groundnut accessions of different botanical varieties after 10 years of storage in Patancheru, Andhra Pradesh, India. Notes are presented on the regeneration requirements of the stored seeds.",
